<br>
Dazzling the audience.. Charming the audience.. Humbling the audience, or confounding them. No, none of that she could do. But she was almost sure she could do something else - that she could capture their imagination and scare them. But she somewhat doubted they would be interested in that. Still, she took note. Perhaps  she would find the time to go.<br>
