<br>
The prizes have been doubled again, so now the winner of the contest will be awarded <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>4000</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> platinum coins! Yes you heard it right, four thousands of shiny coins for the best Storyteller! <br>
<br>
The runner up will receive 800 coins a worthy prize indeed!<br>
<br>
Please remember that if you want to participate, you must sign up. If you are not absolutely sure, that you will be able to attend, please do sign up - just let us know that the unexpected may occur.<br>
<br>
The jurors for the event will be announced promptly as well as all the details of the contest schedule.<br>
<br>
Hurray for the Storytellers!<br>
