Greetings fellow story-tellers, whopper-deliverers, tall-tale-narrators, yarnspinners, and raconteurs (this last word I purchased from a word-smith in Ak'Anon). I am a bard of very little in the way of real talent but a WHOLE lot of chutzpah! (purchased this word from a somewhat sullied dwarf in a tavern). I would be honored to be allowed the high honor of competing in your contest! I would be proud to represent the Circle of Sisters and Clan of Brothers in this gala (bought from a koada'dal poet) contest and hope that I may be among the finalists chosen.<br>
<br>
